Neighborhood Pharmacy app for patients in Seneca area, South Carolina. Please register with us to enjoy wide range of services provided by us.

App features:
New patient registration
Online refill request


SERVICES WE OFFER

Prescriptions: Our app features online refills and also our highly trained staff are only a call away to discuss with you about your prescriptions, side -effects, drug interactions, adherence issues and refills.

Immunizations
Our certified and experienced Immunizing Pharmacists can provide recommendations and administer all essential vaccines including Flu, Pneumonia, Shingles, Tdap and several travel vaccines.

OTC products
We offer a range of Over the counter products and recommendations in Essential oils, Nutraceuticals, Natural medicine, Diabetic supplies and home medical equipment.

Delivery
Home delivery options available. Call us for more information at 864-886-1096.

Drive Thru
Save time by using our convenient Drive-Thru window today.

CONTACT US

Fax: 864-973-9100
